// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0068 — Mass File Rename (dispossessor)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7c9157bf-4814-5051-a408-92e08318e718

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
